snippet.title: Space Chef - Official Trailer | Future of Play Direct 2023
snippet.description:
Space Chef is a 2D open-world action adventure where you’ll explore alien planets, harvest exotic ingredients, and cook cosmic cuisine. Watch the latest trailer for a peek at the alien worlds and more from Space Chef, coming to PC.

#GameTrailers #SummerOfGaming
